                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {},
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "scroll-timeline"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": " is set on the scroller that will provide the timeline. The starting scroll position represents 0% progress and the ending scroll position represents 100% progress. If the 0% position and 100% position coincide (i.e., the scroll container has no overflow to scroll), the timeline is inactive."
